This is the "Brain of Brains." It transforms Velm from a single-project tool into a **Multiversal Operating System**. In a world of microservices and nomadic agents, the Fleet Commander provides the single **Governance Axis**. It scries the `Event-Lattice` (Turn 11) to aggregate real-time vitals, adjudicates the `Metabolic Tax` across AWS and OVH, and allows the Architect to broadcast a single "Will" (e.g., "Harden all perimeters") across 1,000 disparate repositories simultaneously.

By applying the **7-Pillar Taxonomy**, the `CausalLinker` now identifies this as the `governance-authority`. It @provides the `fleet-orchestrator` and @requires the `neural-backbone` to communicate with its vessels.

